Hi everyone,



I have a problem with the openstudio component. I get an almost empty file please find it attached. I got an old file previously fixed by Mostapha ([http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/hb-export-t...](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/hb-export-to-open-studio-not-working)) this one worked but when I updated the file with the new version I got back the 13.9 kb .osm file. 



Am I missing something? Am I doing something wrong ?

Please advise

replies.body: Hi Mohamed, You have made couple of mistake in assigning the materials. You're assigning Window materials to walls which makes the component to fail the zones. Find the fixed file attached. [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/Uf5Jdma8M31JrYw42M9syBD0O*RMMIckfC1Foh0JEpp2GYuhonyRKyGYi0gQHR5GMtDXeN1DY9Vbi3lCfHn-5OuUwdkz5X3L/OpenStudioModel.PNG)
